Q Government could have amended the tobacco law A Amendment will bring in an adverse impact rather Government facilitation is just temporary It maintain status quo when the situation gets better But amendment means we are making it permanent That s awful

I have seen many people comparing with drugs The issue is completely different Drugs are a contraband substance It was banned completely But tobacco was not People can legally smoke but they cannot use drugs even during the normal situation
When the government s decision has restricted the movement of people to buy products it becomes their mandate to facilitate access to tobacco products for those consumers

Q Then how about other drugs Can the government facilitate to supply the drugs as well A What we need to understand is that tobacco and its products were never banned It was just controlled People were allowed to bring in and consume

Also the Constitution gives the right to trade and business But our shops and businesses are closed Can we say the government is amending the Constitution No we can xe2 x80 x99t The government is doing all they can for the benefit of us
We can xe2 x80 x99t say government here is amending the Constitution Can we Everyone feels okay to be staying home and not moving around

Q Does it mean that the Government has unilaterally amended the Tobacco Act A People cannot single out the distribution of tobacco products alone For example this lockdown also violates our fundamental right to movement enshrined in our Constitution This is rather serious
There are hundreds of people out there who can t live without smoking We can t ignore that group of people

Q As per the Constitution it seems like unlawful Not sure which provision of Constitution he refers to A People just make noise on this particular product They are silent on alcohol meat and other commodities which has similar negative impacts

Some questions I get during the lockdown And some points I made it Q What s your stand on government allowing the Duty Free Shop to distribute tobacco and tobacco products A Completely okay It xe2 x80 x99s like the government facilitating to make access to any other essential items
